{"tid":1059552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"三國殺算唔算無最好玩既卡game","createTime":"2019-03-13T07:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T02:56:42.000Z","uid":187585,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e72c29fd91d723e0a0e2154bcf2a671aaa537a92","tid":1059552,"uid":187585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"玩身分又要估邊個反 邊個係忠臣 內奸又要玩到好似忠既仆街 係亦忠亦反期間殺害身邊所有人 完勝！<br />\n國戰不分敵我 先殺暗將 仆街原來係隊友 又要用腦出謀獻策 又要確保自己屹立不敗之地 坐山觀虎鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n單挑1.1 要簡邊隻將可以剋對方 對自己有優勢 <br />\n2打2 配合隊友 神組合屌打對方<br />\n3打3 主帥及兩名前鋒 都由主帥決策<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申非打手"},{"pid":"029da53aa2bcfbc3fe8a2543783aa99f9f8de769","tid":1059552,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:57:08.000Z","msg":"其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284bb938a93e4ded1e70d261bfe8c8591c2d1c61","tid":1059552,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"有平衡之下係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd34dffa3826e9dbd4d462769188da1d1800c7a","tid":1059552,"uid":50889,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"我同 fd 面對面玩一場 8 人身份場要成粒鐘<br />\n搞到早死果啲人好無聊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085594921874966a2368875ad613b6ffc5e433ac","tid":1059552,"uid":82816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"未玩壞之前就係<br />\n土豪將就算你搵埋alphago黎打都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d268e7276540b3c9e23e823a18193c2200d037","tid":1059552,"uid":187585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"029da53aa2bcfbc3fe8a2543783aa99f9f8de769","tid":1059552,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:57:08.000Z","